com.worldpay.library.webservices.services.authtokens

Class AuthTokenCreateRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.worldpay.library.webservices.services.BaseService
      • com.worldpay.library.webservices.services.ServiceRequest
        • com.worldpay.library.webservices.services.authtokens.AuthTokenCreateRequest

  • public class AuthTokenCreateRequest
extends ServiceRequest
    This object is sent when requesting an authorization token from the server so that other APIs can be used. Only one ID and Key/PIN should be set, based on the processing gateway the application is to use
